&lt;li&gt;Optimize site merchandising and online engagement - ensuring strong CX experience and functionality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead promotional planning, product launches, and seasonal campaigns in collaboration with Brand, Design and Media teams&lt;/li&gt;
