ing leadership across ERP platforms (e.g., Cin7) and future system implementations&lt;br&gt;● Establish and lead operational performance management, including KPI definition, reporting, and analysis&lt;br&gt;(e.g., Inbound Accuracy, and On-Time In-Full), driving data-informed decision-making and continuous&lt;br&gt;improvement&lt;br&gt;● Oversee inventory accuracy and health, including Inventory on Hand, slow-moving and obsolete inventory,&lt;br&gt;and revenue recovery through retail compliance and chargeback management&lt;br&gt
